des:
Vistapro Smart will allow you to easily control your outdoor lighting smart devices.

Simply create scenes or use voice control to set up your perfect outdoor lighting experience.

You can simply ask Alexa to control your lights. After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “VistaPro Smart” app and then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “VistaPro Smart” app and change appropriate names for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app and then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search for the “VistaPro Smart” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “VistaPro Smart” skill, and you'll be navigated to “VistaPro Smart” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Once all of the setup is finished, you’ll be able to voice control your VistaPro Smart fixtures with commands such as:
* Alexa, turn on light 
* Alexa, turn off light
* Alexa, dim light to 40%
* Alexa, set light to blue
